fr.ybonnel.csvengine.annotation
Annotation Type CsvColumn

@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=FIELD)
public @interface CsvColumn

Annotation used on attribute of class which is a column of CSV file

French : Annotation utilisée pour représenté une colonne csv.

Author:
ybonnel

Required Element Summary
 String value
          Name of the CSV Column.
 
Optional Element Summary
 Class<? extends AdapterCsv<?>> adapter
          Adapter to use to transform the Object into String and reverse.
 boolean mandatory
          Describe if the column is mandatory (false by default).
 int order
          Order of the column (useful to be sure that column are always write in a defined order).
 CsvParam[] params
          Parametes of the adapter, no parameters by default.
